Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
