Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98119,99537}Because I'm your dream girl…?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101080,102707}If you say it just one more time…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:44.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103791,104751}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107712,108796}You resemble…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110089,111049}You…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111382,114260}…resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:02:00.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116262,120850}MOM'S SECRET!\NA FEMALE THIEF'S VENGEANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123269,126564}You resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129859,131778}The girl Asuka Jr. likes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132987,134405}He likes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134614,135740}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137325,139869}Oh, Meimi! Class is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140203,141996}You were like that\Nthroughout the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142163,143289}That's why the Sister was angry…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143373,145166}…and gave only you homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:26.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145583,146542}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148002,148961}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149128,150546}…Asuka Jr.'s words…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150713,152507}…keep repeating in my head…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153257,156260}I've got an idea! Asuka Jr.!\NWhy don't you help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:38.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156344,158221}You can finish it\Nin 15 minutes, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:45.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164435,165520}Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165645,167980}It's worthless\Nunless you do it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168981,170191}– Oh, no.\N– They're going to start up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170983,172193}That's all right, Ryoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.36,0:02:53.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172360,173319}What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173736,174862}I'll do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175113,176739}– What..?\N– The fight didn't start…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180201,183037}You resemble the girl\NI can't stop thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183579,185540}Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185623,186666}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:12.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188418,192046}You know the crown of the sun,\Nthe Prominence Crown, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:16.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192755,196217}Yeah. It's showing\Nat the F Art Museum, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:19.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196718,199220}Don't you think\NSt. Tail is going to target it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201180,202473}What? What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:27.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203766,207061}There's a treasure\Nlying at the end of the rainbow…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208020,209272}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209897,212150}The Prominence Crown\Nwas owned…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212233,214235}…by the Astoria Royal Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214360,215820}These are the words\Nfrom the Royal Family's crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216487,217447}On this crown…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217530,220116}…there are seven jewels…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220199,222618}…which, people said,\Nwere from the end of a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222869,223870}Garnet…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224078,225037}Topaz…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225496,227623}Emerald and sapphire…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227749,229417}They are seven colored jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229709,230877}How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231335,233755}Only the ruby,\Nwhich was in the center,…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234088,236382}…has been missing for some time.\NIt's a famous story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236966,238634}Some say it was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238926,240970}But no one knows\Nexactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241596,242555}However…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242764,245516}The ruby has resurfaced\Nafter over a ten-year absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245767,247852}I've heard it will go on auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248186,250813}How would it be possible\Nfor St. Tail to pass it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250980,252648}I've got the front-page article!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253483,255401}You did good research.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255902,258529}I've seen the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258780,260948}Wow! I should go to see it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261073,262033}Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263284,265745}Unfortunately St. Tail has\Nno intention of stealing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:26.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265995,266954}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269791,270750}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271292,273503}Meimi's father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273836,277089}Thank you for being\Na good friend to Meimi, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277840,279300}Not at all. The feeling is mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280510,282136}Today I came here to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282220,284347}What?\NIs something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284430,285389}As a matter of fact…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287600,290937}The other day, all three of us\Nwent to the F Art Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292063,294690}But since we saw\Nthe Prominence Crown…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294816,298194}…Eimi, my wife,\Nhas been a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299153,300947}She seems depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303074,306244}What can I do to cheer her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306327,307370}Let's pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308079,310623}I'm sure God will help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312667,314460}Thank you, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321926,323010}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323594,326681}As I suspected, since that day\NMom has been depressed…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326931,328891}You, too, are depressed…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329308,331310}Your father said so\Nand is worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331561,333229}Oh, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333729,334689}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335648,337733}Enough about me.\NI'll ask Mom to her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337900,339026}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:40.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340027,340987}Meimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346742,347702}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348327,349704}Mom, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350037,351497}Does the reason\Nyou're depressed…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351706,354667}…have anything to do\Nwith the Prominence Crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360298,361549}Thank you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362008,363050}You've noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364260,365219}You're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365845,368139}Maybe it's about time\Nfor me to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:23.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382278,383237}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383362,385489}You know I was once\Na mysterious thief, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385615,386574}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388200,391245}It was in a town very far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392496,394373}I was called\N"Mysterious Thief Lucifer."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395291,396876}It meant a devil\Nthat had fallen from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405009,407261}I was a mean thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:52.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408512,412308}I stole things from innocent\Npeople time after time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412683,413935}…and became\Nthe talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:58.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415019,418189}Did you say you wanted me\Nto walk in your footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418397,419649}Oh, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419815,422693}The thing I want you to take\Nis my athletic ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423861,425821}You don't do bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426280,427698}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438960,439919}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:24.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440252,444090}Originally I started to do it\Nto test my athletic ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:29.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445466,449553}But later I discovered\Nthat I couldn't stop being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450513,451514}For what reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451806,453599}Did you have someone who\Npursued you with all of his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454100,456560}– What?\N– Oh, nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463567,465111}My rival showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466320,468489}I still get irritated\Nwhen I think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:52.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468698,472118}A despicable mysterious\Nfemale thief showed up in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473035,475079}She enjoyed\Ndoing things for spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475162,476998}She targeted whatever item\NI was planning to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477123,478708}She was like a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479500,482461}Oh, Mom.\NYou're so competitive…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483295,484672}But one night…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491804,493347}…while I was trying to get away\Nfrom the police…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493431,495307}…I hurt my ankle because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497309,499395}I was in a desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502982,505735}Then someone hid me\Nwithout any questions…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505901,507111}It was Dad, wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510573,513200}He was living in a small\Napartment and training…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513325,514452}…to be a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514869,516829}I don't have it.\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517580,519707}I'm poor and I don't\Nhave any medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519915,521292}It hurts, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521375,522710}It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522918,524253}But don't make so much noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524920,526505}If they fiind me, you'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526589,527757}Oh, I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528174,529592}Hey! Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530259,531260}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531343,532303}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532470,533471}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542563,544023}I can only do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544440,546567}But it's good for hiding, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:18.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557995,558954}Since then…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:22.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559747,562750}Whenever we met,\Nhe gave me an armful of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563000,563959}Only flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:28.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565377,568672}That's the only magic\Nhe could do at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583437,585189}I was happy…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586273,588901}…because he always did\Nall that he could do…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589235,591278}…and he tried to make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592154,593239}When I watched him like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:55.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593739,595407}…I started to think…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:58.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595616,598369}…of the stupid things\NI had been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599328,601789}And I stopped being a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613384,615094}I planned on returning\Nall of the things I had stolen…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615511,617847}…to their rightful owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618514,620850}At least I was planning to do so…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621725,622726}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:26.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622810,626647}…the one thing I couldn't return\Nwas the Prominence Crown's ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628149,631110}On the way to return it,\Nthat other woman took it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632820,633988}And that's how it ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634905,636365}When I saw the crown…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636740,638284}…I remembered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638868,640286}Cheer up, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640870,642079}I'm not going to tell Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645916,647793}Dad knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648752,651046}As always\Nhe doesn't mention it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:05.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661473,665186}Seira. I'm going\Nto get the Crown's ruby back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665603,667688}The auction place is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667771,668939}…the same place as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670191,671275}So this time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671442,673194}…I don't think\Nyou should go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:14.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673777,674862}Besides, I'm sure Asuka has…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:16.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674987,676822}…all of the information\Nabout the place…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677573,679033}I've found the warehouse…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679283,682369}…where they're keeping\Nthe ruby until the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696217,697176}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697843,698802}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699678,700679}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702306,703849}"Tomorrow night,\NI'm going to the R Warehouse…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703974,705809}…to take the 'Star Ruby.'
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706101,707061}– St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:48.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707770,708729}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709230,710648}As expected, she's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712983,715611}Asuka Jr. is\Nin love with someone…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718197,720074}What should I do, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723827,725746}You haven't gone home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:06.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725871,726872}Neither have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731001,733212}Excuse me, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:24.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739760,744640}Hello! I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop near this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745349,747017}Please come by\Nwith your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749270,750771}Oh, my…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751855,754191}How cute! You're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:38.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755109,758654}Hello there! I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759238,760948}Please come!\NI'll be expecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761240,763242}Hello, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763867,766537}I guess it's better\Nif you're not seen with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768580,770207}I've never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780551,781635}This is for your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781719,784305}You can peek\Nonly if you can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787308,788267}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788934,791645}I didn't do it for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:13.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792646,793897}Practice… practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806910,809872}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815169,816128}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818589,819548}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821884,824470}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839026,840444}Good luck, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840694,842988}You can leave it to me!\NIt's for my dad and mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:08.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845199,848410}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866178,867137}There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867304,868597}That must be the Star Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869556,871225}Where is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874019,876063}Today is the day I'll catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877272,878232}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878357,879316}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879441,880609}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884780,885781}Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886073,887658}It's too easy…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888158,889118}Where is the security?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893330,896166}The owner of the jewel…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896500,898544}…refused the security\Nin the warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899294,900254}Are they outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910639,911723}I've got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912182,913600}You won't escape today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913725,914685}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914810,915769}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:16.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915978,916979}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:23.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919731,923735}I'm sorry, but you're the last\Nperson I want to catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934913,936373}At last I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:42.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937708,942087}We've put the Star Ruby\Non auction to draw you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943046,944214}The Mysterious Thief Lucifer…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944506,945799}We've discovered\Nthe clue to finding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968489,970491}You're the last person\NI want to catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974328,975287}I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976538,978790}I wonder why I want to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980542,982377}At first, I just wanted to catch her…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983962,986131}When you showed up,\NI was excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987049,988008}But then…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989009,990677}…I didn't want\Nanyone else to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999394,1000687}From that moment on…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109713,1112799}There's a treasure lying\Nat the end of the rainbow…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115677,1117179}I don't remember\Nwhich royal family it was…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117471,1119848}…but the end of the rainbow\Ncan't exist physically…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120641,1121850}Oh, shoot! I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168271,1169731}At the end of the rainbow…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170691,1171733}…is a treasure…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:37.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176863,1177948}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:41.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178490,1181076}Don't tell me he spent\Nthe whole night in the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182953,1184121}What's the matter?!
